WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.001

00:00:00.997 --> 00:00:04.963
How do you explain
when things don't go as we assume?

00:00:25.030 --> 00:00:27.196
They have the same access to the same talent,

00:00:27.230 --> 00:00:28.196
the same agencies,
00:00:28.230 --> 00:00:30.097
the same consultants, the same media.

00:00:30.130 --> 00:00:33.630
Then why is it that they seem to have something different?

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:31.500
Exactly.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:46.500
Exactly.
